                        <h1>Opening of Technology Centre Mongstad</h1>
                    
                
            </div>
        </div>
    

<div class="documentBody" id="Tekstinnhold">
    
    
    
        <div>
            

<div>
	<p><strong>On Monday 7 May, Prime Minister Jens Stoltenberg opened the world’s largest and most advanced facility for testing and improving CO<sub>2 </sub>capture technologies<sub>.</sub></strong></p>
<p>Technology Centre Mongstad will test various methods of capturing CO<sub>2</sub> from the refinery and the combined heat and power plant at Mongstad to determine which is the best and most cost-effective.</p>
<ul>
<li>&nbsp;<a href="/en/dep/smk/Whats-new/Speeches-and-articles/statsministeren/statsminister_jens_stoltenberg/2012/technology-centre-mongstad.html?id=681066">Read the Prime Minister’s speech here</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
